    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Stridulatory organs of Adapantus (Adapantus) excavatus (A–D) and Adapantus (Neoadapantus) affluens (E–F; from Naskrecki, 2008a, reproduced with permission). A tegmina in situ, B stridulatory file, C, E left tegmen, from above, D, F right tegmen, from above. Scale C, D 5 mm." ;
